":2430304,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:19:47.000Z","msg":"忠誠勇毅？！<br />\n仆街至係，肥過隻閪，跪住嚟舐，瞓覺最威，驚青過雞！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6TPoo8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6TPoo8e.jpg&h=1dc04d27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ad9d27012a8abd2356c554e1d015b9c69bc3fbf","tid":2430304,"uid":26672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:21:17.000Z","msg":"Live都有得抹黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594f5049ec2b7fccefcba1d28e69f15d0cba0f20","tid":2430304,"uid":46595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:23:46.000Z","msg":"721講一世都解釋唔到"},{"pid":"9eb5dc45fb893588a524a3148c8880667d098a42","tid":2430304,"uid":292424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"594f5049ec2b7fccefcba1d28e69f15d0cba0f20","tid":2430304,"uid":46595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:23:46.000Z","msg":"721講一世都解釋唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:28:04.000Z","msg":"果度係國家都唔同法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解要解釋"},{"pid":"11b6a436d210f2205e713e5ef8a3f57cd5af8157","tid":2430304,"uid":127695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:35:23.000Z","msg":"最佳閱讀獎"},{"pid":"579960352db54e88100338ad1166c9dcfd80c95b","tid":2430304,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:36:36.000Z","msg":"講事實你又嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949f2e7d60153e3ac7d3d006bb900865e4d9ad75","tid":2430304,"uid":45975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:38:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"86965cb238eb63ceec93343a40ea63b7060b34aa","tid":2430304,"uid":326280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:44:11.000Z","msg":"天天寫 封封寫滿六百句的我愛你